<td tEditID="c1r1" style=" background-color:#FFFFFF; bEditID:r3st1; color:#000000; bLabel:main; font-size:12pt; font-family:arial;" aEditID="c1r1" locked="0" >
<![CDATA[<div style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><div style=""><div style=""><div style=""><div style=""><div style="font-size: 12pt;"><div style="font-size: 12pt;"><div style="font-size: 12pt;"><div style="font-size: 12pt;"><div style="font-size: 12pt;"><font face="arial" style="font-size: 12pt;">Hi {!Contact.FirstName},<br></font><br style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">Thank you for getting in touch with Kingsbridge.</span><br style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><br style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">Because we operate the Direct Debits payment schedule over 10 months for your 12-month policy duration,&nbsp;</span><b style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">we’re happy to confirm that all the payments for your policy have been made</b><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">.</span><br style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><br style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">To honour your cancellation request, please rest assured that&nbsp;</span><u style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">your policy has now been removed from auto-renewal</u><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">&nbsp;and no further payments will be taken. Your policy will remain in place until&nbsp;</span><i style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">DDMMYYYY</i><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">.</span><br style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><br style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">If you still&nbsp;</span><u style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">wish to proceed with your cancellation, please carefully review the information below and confirm by replying to this email within 7 calendar days.</u><br style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><br style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><b style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">Important information regarding your insurance cover</b><br style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><br style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><i style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">(Use if holding PI)&nbsp;</i><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">Your package of insurance includes Professional Indemnity cover. This element of the policy works on a ‘claims made’ basis, meaning&nbsp;</span><u style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">you must have cover in place at the time of the claim and not at the time of the incident for your policy to provide cover</u><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">.</span><br style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><br style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><i style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">(Use if holding PI)&nbsp;</i><b style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><u>If you choose to cancel your Kingsbridge insurance policy and do not hold alternative cover elsewhere your business will not be covered</u></b><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">&nbsp;against claims of negligence.</span><br style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><br style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">Any claims for the&nbsp;</span><i style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">(delete as appropriate)&nbsp;</i><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">Public Liability, Employers’ Liability, Contract Works, Own Plant and Hired in Plant elements for the time your policy was active&nbsp;</span><i style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">(DD MMM YYYY to DD MMM YYYY)&nbsp;</i><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">can be notified to insurers. Please refer to your policy wording&nbsp; for full information.</span><br style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><br style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">Whether you’re currently insured with Kingsbridge or not, our customer service team is always here to help. Please don’t hesitate to reply to this email if you need any further information on any of the above.</span><br style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><font face="arial" style="font-size: 12pt;"><br>Kind regards,<br></font><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><br>{!User.FirstName}<br></span><span style="font-size: 12pt;">Customer Service Team<br></span><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><br>E:&nbsp;</span><a href="mailto:customersupport@kingsbridge.co.uk" style="font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">customersupport@kingsbridge.co.uk</a><br style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;">T: 01242 808 740</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div>]]></td>
</tr>
</table>